{
  "text": "It is known [CITATION_1] 48] in combinatorial analysis that the Catalan numbers C n for n \u2265 0 form a sequence of natural numbers that occur in tree enumeration problems such as \"In how many ways can a regular n-gon be divided into n \u2212 2 triangles if different orientations are counted separately?\" whose solution is the Catalan number C n\u22122 . The Catalan numbers C n can be generated by",
